on the scoot
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number:
Definition:a drinking session or party; a bash, espec. in phrase on the scoot, on the booze, on the spree
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
